Features 
=================

The features selected for this database are from five smartwatch built-in sensors signals:
accelerometer, linear acceleration sensor, gyroscope, and gravity sensor with 3-axial raw signals, and heart rate sensor for beats per minute (bpm) in one dimension signal.


'acc' : accelerometer
'Lac' : linear acceleration sensor
'gro' : gyroscope
'gvt' : gravity sensor
'htr' : heart rate sensor

'x, y, z' : 3-axial signals in the X, Y and Z directions.

mean: Mean value
std : Standard deviation
med : Median value 
p25 : 25th percentile
p75 : 75th percentile



